message.content: cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.FL, cs.ET - The workshop focuses on the synthesis of computing systems, which involves the development of algorithms and tools for automating the creation of software, hardware, embedded, and cyberphysical systems. This topic is closely related to several sub-categories of computer science, including logic in computer science (cs.LO), programming languages (cs.PL), software engineering (cs.SE), formal languages and automata theory (cs.FL), and emerging technologies (cs.ET).
